\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\size large
Integrative (
\begin_inset Formula $H_i$
\end_inset

) – the biota living in a given time and location represent a full integration of all relevant environmental and biological factors at their proper space time scales and so in effect characterises the full system-level concept of "habitat space" 
\end_layout

